snippet.textDisplay: What a great lecture! I followed along and actually knew most of the answers. I'm indirectly in Medicine and was able to piece together my current knowledge with actual clinical application. And with a few more of your lectures, I could take the M-CAT!! LOL! Great job!! I wish more instructors were as good as you are!
